OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1784231286
OL,3,CWhat is local government
OL,4,Creorganisation?
OL,6,FPlans have been announced to
OL,7,Fcompletely overhaul Devon's political
OL,8,Fmap under the Local Government
OL,9,FReorganisation model.
OL,11,FThe 11 existing councils, that run
OL,12,Feverything from social services,
OL,13,Fhousing, bin collections and
OL,14,Flibraries, will become four larger
OL,15,Fcouncils.
OL,17,FIt follows proposals from councils
OL,18,Facross Devon last year and a public
OL,19,Fconsultation undertaken by Government
OL,20,Fearlier this year.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
