OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1784231286
OL,3,CWhat is local government
OL,4,Creorganisation?
OL,6,FThe new four unitary model also forms
OL,7,Fpart of a wider programme to replace
OL,8,Fthe current two-tier system of county
OL,9,Fand district councils with unitary
OL,10,Fauthorities.
OL,12,FWhich areas will be affected?
OL,14,FIt would see Ivybridge and other
OL,15,Fparishes in the South Hams form part
OL,16,Fof a Greater Plymouth Council.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
