OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1784231286
OL,3,CWhat is local government
OL,4,Creorganisation?
OL,6,FExeter will also expand, taking over
OL,7,Fthe running of towns such as Exmouth
OL,8,Fand Dawlish. While the new boundary of
OL,9,FTorbay Council will stretch to include
OL,10,Ftowns and villages like Newton Abbot
OL,11,Fand Teignmouth.
OL,13,FThe rest of Devon will be covered by
OL,14,Fone new council, called Devon Coast
OL,15,Fand Countryside.
OL,17,FWhat do the changes mean?
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
