OL,3,CWhat is local government
OL,4,Creorganisation?
OL,6,FThe shake-up, proposed by Plymouth and
OL,7,FExeter City councils, is aimed at
OL,8,Fsimplifying how local government works
OL,9,Facross Devon by creating councils that
OL,10,Fare responsible for the full range of
OL,11,Flocal government services within their
OL,12,Fareas.
OL,14,FFor most residents, Devon County
OL,15,FCouncil handles major issues, such as
OL,16,Feducation and roads, while smaller
OL,17,Fdistrict councils handle local issues,
OL,18,Fsuch as bins and planning.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
