CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1784231286
OL,3,CWhat is local government
OL,4,Creorganisation?
OL,6,FThe changes will mean Devon County
OL,7,FCouncil disappears, along with the
OL,8,Fdistrict councils, to be replaced by
OL,9,Ffour 'mega' authorities that cover
OL,10,Feverything.
OL,12,FSupporters say it will make things
OL,13,Fsimpler, cut duplication and create a
OL,14,Fstronger council able to deliver major
OL,15,Fservices including social care.
OL,17,FWhat do councils think?
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
