OL,3,CWhat is local government
OL,4,Creorganisation?
OL,6,FThe leader of Devon County Council
OL,7,Fsays the plans will mean "council tax
OL,8,Fwill go up" and the "quality of
OL,9,Fservices will go down".
OL,11,FCouncillor Julian Brazil told ITV
OL,12,FNews: "The people of Devon are being
OL,13,Fbetrayed. It's a deceitful decision
OL,14,Fdriven by political gerrymandering.
OL,16,F"I don't know why they bothered even
OL,17,Fconsulting us if all they were going
OL,18,Fto do is listen to their mates in
OL,19,FPlymouth and Exeter and neglect the
OL,20,Fvast majority of people in Devon".
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1784231286
OL,3,CWhat is local government
OL,4,Creorganisation?
OL,6,FHe estimates a #250 increase per
OL,7,Fhousehold, which he says will be
OL,8,F"consumed into the urban areas".
OL,10,F"Rural Devon is going to suffer
OL,11,Fmassively".
OL,13,FMeanwhile, the deputy leader of East
OL,14,FDevon District Council, Councillor
OL,15,FJohn Loudoun said: "There's no
OL,16,Fintention that there will be
OL,17,Fredundancies".
OL,19,FHe says they're looking at a "transfer
OL,20,Fof services".
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1784231286
OL,3,CWhat is local government
OL,4,Creorganisation?
OL,6,F"Clearly, there will be one or two
OL,7,Fsavings to be made at a senior level -
OL,8,Fotherwise, we hope that both staff and
OL,9,Fpublic will see a continuance of
OL,10,Fservices at present".
OL,12,FPlymouth City Council are supportive
OL,13,Fof the changes. Councillor Tudor Evans
OL,14,Fsaid: "The Government announced today
OL,15,Fits desire to see council tax bills
OL,16,Fnot going up.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
