CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1784231286
OL,3,CWhat is local government
OL,4,Creorganisation?
OL,6,F"Removing a whole tier of local
OL,7,Fgovernment should see savings - it
OL,8,Fmight mean utilising that money spent
OL,9,Fon the administration of local
OL,10,Fservices".
OL,12,FWhen will the changes start?
OL,14,FThe new councils won't be in place
OL,15,Funtil April 2028, although the
OL,16,Ftransition will start soon as it will
OL,17,Ftake some time to implement.
OL,19,FWhere else is the unitary model being
OL,20,Fimplemented?
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
