OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1784231286
OL,3,CWhat is local government
OL,4,Creorganisation?
OL,6,FThe government has announced major
OL,7,Fchanges to the layout of councils in
OL,8,FGloucestershire, with plans to move
OL,9,Fthe county to a single unitary
OL,10,Fauthority.
OL,12,FIt will replace the county council and
OL,13,Fall six district and borough councils.
OL,14,FIt's thought that local elections
OL,15,Fwould go ahead in May next year, with
OL,16,Fthe new changes taking effect from
OL,17,FApril 2028.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/10
